47:28.146 --> 47:30.615
WHAT THE FUCK'S GOING ON?

47:30.648 --> 47:32.918
ARE YOU SCREWING WITH ME,
SONNY-BOY?

47:32.951 --> 47:38.256
- NO, I'M NOT SCREWING
WITH YOU.

47:38.289 --> 47:41.426
