TO HOLD HIM?

47:41.459 --> 47:43.528
- OH, I--

47:43.561 --> 47:48.366
IT'S BEEN A WHILE, YOU KNOW,
SINCE I HELD A BABY, BUT...

47:48.399 --> 47:50.969
YEAH.

47:56.607 --> 47:59.077
HI.

48:05.650 --> 48:07.986
